Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.74,0:00:28.03,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,When I close my eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.82,0:00:29.91,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I hear the waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.95,0:00:32.62,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I see the deep\Nblue of the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.45,0:00:38.29,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Filled with the scent of\Nsummer that never ends...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.96,0:00:40.54,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,in these hollow,\Ndrifting days...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.97,0:00:54.93,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.81,0:00:57.89,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,met that person...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.52,0:01:01.27,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,with eyes like the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.57,0:01:12.91,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,♪ Please, let it end... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.91,0:01:14.78,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,♪ Take away everything. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.20,0:01:18.95,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,♪ Devour the pain\Nand loneliness. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.84,0:01:35.39,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,♪ I remained stagnant,\Njust like that day. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.64,0:01:38.22,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,♪ A light pierced through ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.22,0:01:41.23,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,♪ my dark, empty days. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.48,0:01:43.39,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,♪ The color of the deep sea, ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.40,0:01:46.06,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,♪ atop the fleeting bubbles ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.61,0:01:48.36,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,♪ It still gouges my chest... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.36,0:01:50.23,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,♪ Wrapped in the\Nclinging scent of summer. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.24,0:01:52.91,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,♪ I don't want to\Nforget — and yet... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.74,0:01:57.83,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,♪ Before you arrived...\NI split this fruit. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.04,0:02:00.83,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,♪ With those hands,\Nwith that desire. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.25,0:02:05.54,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,♪ I want you to guide\Nthese restrained arms. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.92,0:02:08.67,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,♪ Devour my flesh, my heart. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.13,0:02:12.26,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,♪ Make it come true. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.97,0:02:16.55,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,♪ Ah..., ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.55,0:02:20.31,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,♪ just wait a little longer. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.27,0:02:24.35,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,♪ Ah... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.35,0:02:27.98,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,♪ who was it that\Naimed for me? ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.67,0:04:14.84,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,... I dont wanna go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.68,0:04:22.14,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Oh! Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.35,0:04:23.72,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.10,0:04:25.60,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Oh, heading out, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.19,0:04:30.69,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Wait for me, big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.69,0:04:33.02,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hurry up! We're gonna be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.02,0:04:34.23,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Come on, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.90,0:04:38.28,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Big broooother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.70,0:04:40.20,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Wait for meee!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.74,0:04:42.78,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, Hinako!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.20,0:04:46.54,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Dad and Mom are waiting too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.38,0:04:54.84,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.84,0:04:57.51,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Looks like it'll be\Nhot again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.93,0:05:03.85,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'm stopping by\Nthe convenience store.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.97,0:05:05.47,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'll grab a drink too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.43,0:05:09.77,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I hate summer...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.27,0:05:12.73,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sad things...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:15.73,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Painful things...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.32,0:05:22.24,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,These are all that come\Nto mind when it arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.24,0:05:29.37,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I wish that summer would just...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.71,0:05:32.04,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,end already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.23,0:05:53.60,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Just now, I think something...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.19,0:05:56.02,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,was in the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.15,0:05:59.32,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,A fish...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.69,0:06:00.61,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.57,0:06:03.20,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It looked too big, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.54,0:06:11.79,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.21,0:06:17.17,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It's almost like...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.46,0:06:20.55,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,the deep sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.26,0:06:22.59,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,so clear and pure...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:25.26,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Her eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.47,0:06:30.22,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It's fine to let yourself be\Ncaptivated by the sea, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.60,0:06:34.10,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,If you lean out that\Nfar, it's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.23,0:06:40.28,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Ah! It's not like I was going\Nto fall into the sea or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.73,0:06:41.82,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.49,0:06:43.99,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,My apologies then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.82,0:06:45.95,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,She is totally strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.91,0:06:48.12,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I honestly thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.87,0:06:51.33,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You were about\Nto throw yourself in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.59,0:06:59.29,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hinako...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.05,0:07:01.00,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hinako...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.55,0:07:02.26,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hinako...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.01,0:07:04.42,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Please, at least you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.76,0:07:09.72,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.01,0:07:12.60,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I don't know who you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.52,0:07:14.94,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,but don't say things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:17.06,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Did I offend you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.60,0:07:18.90,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.29,0:07:37.62,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Take care...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.51,0:07:49.60,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Hinako!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.01,0:07:51.39,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Morning, Miko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.85,0:07:54.14,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sorry I couldn't walk\Nwith you this morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.60,0:07:55.52,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.77,0:07:56.52,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Overslept?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.94,0:08:01.11,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,No... I fell asleep without hanging\Nmy uniform to dry yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.52,0:08:04.48,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I had to dry it\Nwith a hairdryer—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.48,0:08:06.82,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I seriously thought\NI wouldn't make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.61,0:08:09.91,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Your cold's still not gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.12,0:08:12.83,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,No worries, I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.79,0:08:18.17,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Forget me, Hinako! Were you\Nokay on your own this morning!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.46,0:08:20.46,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You didn't get hassled\Nby any weirdos, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.75,0:08:21.88,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Miko-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.46,0:08:24.92,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm not a kid, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.38,0:08:26.26,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.47,0:08:28.68,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Miko's at it again...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.09,0:08:29.80,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.14,0:08:33.47,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Miko is seriously so\Noverprotective of Hinako.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.93,0:08:35.77,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Come on—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.77,0:08:38.35,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hinako's so clumsy,\NI worry about her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.60,0:08:40.94,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Just the other day, she\Ntripped over nothing at all—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.94,0:08:44.86,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she does\Ntrip over thin air a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.32,0:08:49.20,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Right!? I just can't\Nleave her alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.87,0:08:52.70,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.16,0:08:55.83,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I kinda get where\NMiko's coming from.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.91,0:09:01.17,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Exactly, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.49,0:09:31.78,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hinako...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.36,0:09:33.53,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hinako...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.53,0:09:35.37,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hinako...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.49,0:09:37.45,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hinako!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.04,0:09:40.12,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What's wrong...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.71,0:09:46.63,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.17,0:09:48.05,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Really...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.63,0:09:52.63,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Morning—get back to your seats!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.09,0:09:54.64,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Okaaay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.89,0:10:03.31,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,My heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.94,0:10:05.31,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Ever since that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.15,0:10:08.86,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,it's been sunk at the\Nbottom of the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.78,0:10:16.41,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,The sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.50,0:10:22.62,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.47,0:10:33.22,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Why is it that I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.76,0:10:37.18,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,would think of that\Nperson as the sea...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.89,0:10:39.22,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Why did I feel that way...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.56,0:10:49.23,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Did you watch Mikarin's video?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.36,0:10:51.99,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I did, I did! It was hilarious!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.49,0:10:54.45,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,We've got section\Npractice today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.70,0:10:57.03,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Yeah... hope I can play well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.49,0:10:59.12,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Crap! I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.49,0:11:00.83,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.20,0:11:03.00,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Student council announcement:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.33,0:11:05.75,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Today's council meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.75,0:11:08.13,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,will begin at 4:45 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.34,0:11:11.46,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hinaaaako!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.09,0:11:13.88,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Can we stop by the\Nbookstore on the way home?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.88,0:11:16.43,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,And the convenience store\Ntoo! There's a new dessert!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.64,0:11:17.43,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.55,0:11:18.97,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Mikooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.43,0:11:22.89,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Glad, I made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.06,0:11:23.85,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.85,0:11:26.10,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Mr. Takano from the Math\Nclass says we have to finish
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.10,0:11:29.65,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,worksheets to make up for his missed class.\NProf. Takano is scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.65,0:11:29.69,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Prof. Takano is scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.69,0:11:31.23,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Whaaaaat!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.90,0:11:32.90,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,But I was gonna hang out with Hinako...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.90,0:11:35.03,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,But I was gonna hang out with Hinako...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.03,0:11:38.03,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,And Mr. Yamashita says once you're done,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.03,0:11:39.57,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,report to the guidance office.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.66,0:11:44.04,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,H-Hinakooo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.04,0:11:45.41,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Miko-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.67,0:11:48.67,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna gooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.00,0:11:50.54,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I hate worksheets!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.88,0:11:53.92,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,And Yamashita's totally\Ngonna chew me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.67,0:11:58.43,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,If you don't go, it'll just\Nget worse, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.47,0:12:01.01,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll wait for you\Ntill you're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.10,0:12:03.81,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.81,0:12:04.60,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Wow!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.60,0:12:07.02,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Then I'll finish it in seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.39,0:12:08.35,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.69,0:12:10.48,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Make the skirt longer too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.11,0:12:13.07,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,The choker too! Off with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.07,0:12:13.82,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.40,0:12:16.90,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Hinako—wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.63,0:12:32.13,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I need to kill some\Ntime somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:37.05,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to\Ndo in the classroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.38,0:12:39.93,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll go to the library...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.64,0:12:43.26,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,read a book until\NMiko-chan gets here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.94,0:12:56.94,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.91,0:13:05.04,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,The smell of the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.08,0:13:08.66,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I heard the sound\Nof the waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.04,0:13:11.67,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That's... from this morning—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.10,0:13:29.43,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What am I even doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.44,0:13:33.77,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Still wearing my indoor shoes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.57,0:13:36.15,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I should go back...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.44,0:13:39.90,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Miko-chan might\Nbe done already...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.29,0:13:55.42,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.42,0:13:58.42,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.61,0:14:17.52,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Fou... nd...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.52,0:14:20.32,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,...you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.91,0:14:27.37,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Fou... nd...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.20,0:14:30.41,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,...you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.16,0:14:33.21,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Ahh... such a lovely scent...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.71,0:14:34.50,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.25,0:14:36.63,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What is this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.34,0:14:40.96,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It was worth coming all the\Nway from the West Sea Route.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.55,0:14:43.68,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.22,0:14:48.60,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I was interrupted this morning,\Nbut now I can finally get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.52,0:14:57.52,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.98,0:14:59.98,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,so sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.44,0:15:02.49,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,incredible...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.11,0:15:05.74,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.32,0:15:07.87,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.95,0:15:12.75,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,With this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.17,0:15:19.96,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Me too...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.19,0:15:37.10,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.48,0:15:40.19,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I told you it was dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.07,0:15:45.90,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Y-you... are...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.66,0:15:48.70,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You wretch...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.03,0:15:53.04,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Why is a mermaid here...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.37,0:15:55.41,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,How dare you interfere!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.66,0:15:58.00,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That's my prey!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.67,0:16:00.71,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Stay behind me, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.13,0:16:03.71,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,A lowly sea hag like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.42,0:16:05.51,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Mermaid...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.05,0:16:07.22,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sea hag...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.55,0:16:09.26,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Such a lowly creature,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.51,0:16:11.93,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,talking big, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.44,0:16:21.15,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That is... mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.77,0:16:22.94,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,This girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.28,0:16:27.91,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,belongs to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.91,0:16:35.29,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It was like──
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.58,0:16:38.71,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,A scene straight out of hell──
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.46,0:16:42.04,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,So gruesome,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.88,0:16:44.76,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I couldn't even move a finger—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.30,0:16:49.47,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.68,0:16:53.76,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.89,0:16:57.02,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.27,0:17:03.23,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hinako...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.15,0:17:08.45,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.15,0:17:12.78,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,How do you know my name...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.99,0:17:16.79,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Of course I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.54,0:17:18.50,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.96,0:17:21.12,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I've been searching\Nfor you all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.67,0:17:22.71,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Searching...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.75,0:17:25.05,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Who are you really...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.17,0:17:27.42,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm Shiori.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.51,0:17:29.51,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.88,0:17:32.47,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,came here to eat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.01,0:17:34.76,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hinako...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.56,0:17:38.93,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Your blood and flesh are\Nexceptionally delicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:41.85,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That's why those vulgar\Nfools gather around...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.85,0:17:43.65,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,My heart pounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.77,0:17:46.15,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Without knowing the season.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.15,0:17:47.94,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Like the roar of the tide—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.32,0:17:48.99,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,so loud...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.28,0:17:51.99,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You'll become even more\Ndelicious from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.95,0:17:54.20,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,So until then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.58,0:17:57.12,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll make sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.58,0:17:58.95,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.91,0:18:02.79,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,In these empty\Ndays, filled with the
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.79,0:18:06.00,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,scent of an endless,\Nunseen summer...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.67,0:18:09.30,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,If it's this person who\Nappeared so suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.59,0:18:11.72,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,She might...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.70,0:18:38.16,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.41,0:18:41.37,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.08,0:18:44.00,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It's so hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.92,0:18:52.13,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Miko-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.01,0:18:55.93,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hinako!? Why!? Why\Nare you soaking wet!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.89,0:18:57.64,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.14,0:19:01.02,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,after that, I probably\Ncaused a lot of trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.77,0:19:03.39,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Maybe that's why
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.39,0:19:05.48,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,her cold came back...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.19,0:19:08.98,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Miko-chan may not look like,\Nbut she's got a weak Body...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.40,0:19:10.36,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Isn't that rude!? {Says the same thing as in the sign here}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.36,0:19:12.19,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I hope it doesn't get worse...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.69,0:19:14.86,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Seriously, it's going\Nto be hot again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.16,0:19:16.53,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Shall we go to the\Nsea after school~?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.53,0:19:18.87,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,If we go, we should\Neat something first...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.54,0:19:29.46,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You said...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.34,0:19:33.80,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You'd eat me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.13,0:19:37.05,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Is it really true...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.39,0:19:45.02,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.10,0:19:50.52,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,ah, but I won't eat you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.49,0:19:54.65,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Make sure you treat
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.90,0:19:56.91,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,that wound properly...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.95,0:19:58.91,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.41,0:20:04.20,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Wa... wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.58,0:20:06.54,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What do you mean
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.67,0:20:10.00,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hinako!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.13,0:20:11.84,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hinako? You here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.59,0:20:13.75,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Where'd you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.76,0:20:14.46,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Miko-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.01,0:20:16.63,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hii-na-kooo...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.80,0:20:17.93,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Heyyy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.06,0:20:22.76,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,She's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.23,0:20:26.48,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.65,0:20:38.03,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,About me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.28,0:20:45.20,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You said you'd eat me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.54,0:20:52.25,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Why... yesterday...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.09,0:20:55.01,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.92,0:20:57.59,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,take your seats...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.05,0:21:00.22,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,oh, before homeroom, we've
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.22,0:21:02.01,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,got a transfer\Nstudent to introduce.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.11,0:21:15.53,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,The tide...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.53,0:21:18.40,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,She'll be joining this\Nclass starting today!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.66,0:21:20.91,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,The smell of the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.78,0:21:24.16,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,This is Shiori Oumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.42,0:21:35.59,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I came here to eat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.09,0:21:38.34,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,This person might...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.18,0:21:43.76,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,fulfill my wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.60,0:21:47.27,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,She might...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.36,0:21:56.98,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,let me die...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.61,0:22:03.70,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,♪ Dear... I send\Nyou this LiLy! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.91,0:22:09.91,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,♪ As for my days... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.25,0:22:13.13,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,♪ they pass without\Nchange, quietly repeating. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.54,0:22:15.92,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,♪ Ever since that day\Neverything changed. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.59,0:22:19.21,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,♪ As for my days... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.80,0:22:22.47,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,♪ My heart feels\Nunbearably heavy... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.89,0:22:25.14,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,♪ Yet my body drifts,\Nsoft and weightless. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.51,0:22:29.43,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,♪ Like being drawn\Ntoward a scent.. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.43,0:22:31.69,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,♪ that's just out of reach... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.94,0:22:34.10,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,♪ Those were the days I lived. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.27,0:22:38.27,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,♪ A sudden summer breeze\Nmade white flowers sway, ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.28,0:22:40.82,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,♪ Touching my heart,\Nfragile like a pouch. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.24,0:22:44.49,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,♪ You found me —\Nwith those eyes. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.08,0:22:49.37,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,♪ Dear me... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.37,0:22:52.62,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,♪ The pain I've\Ncarried so long- ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.92,0:22:56.38,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,♪ — is it finally scattering,\Nscattering away? ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.50,0:23:01.88,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,♪ The scenes you showed\Nme — so often beautiful... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.88,0:23:05.55,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,♪ They're blooming...\Nstill blooming, even now. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.26,0:23:08.60,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,♪ A sea so dark it\Nswallows even shadows... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.72,0:23:10.89,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,♪ If it could cradle\Nthe goodbyes.. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.89,0:23:13.73,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,♪ that lost their way...... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.23,0:23:18.02,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I found myself thinking\Nsuch things... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.02,0:23:22.03,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,♪ But then you crossed my\Nmind... and I breathed again. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.32,0:23:24.74,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,♪ Not to the me of today — ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.74,0:23:26.24,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,♪ but to me of that day — ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.24,0:23:28.16,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,♪ I send this lily. ♪
